title: The Cocktail Store
description: Find your favorite cocktail details and explore a wide range of cocktail recipes. This application allows users to search for various cocktails, view detailed information about each, and discover new favorites. Whether you're a cocktail enthusiast or a casual drinker, this app provides a comprehensive cocktail database at your fingertips.

title: MoneyMap
description: Money Map Finance Tracker is a personal finance management tool that helps you track expenses, manage investments, and visualize spending trends. Stay organized with a user-friendly dashboard and gain insights into your financial habits. Explore the project live or check out the source code on GitHub.
